		<!-- message -->
		<div id="post_message_40216">Is the problem the character's inherent power as a monk/shadowdancer/vampire, or is it that he has too many magic items?  Or a little of each?<br />
<br />
And is the player in question a reasonable one, who will work with you on making the character fit in your campaign world, or is he the kind who considers his character (and his character's posessions) to be inviolably holy, and would resent any modification by fiat before play, or modification by somewhat targeted events during play?  <br />
<br />
